main event: The witness observed a bright, car-shaped craft with bluish green lights glide slowly across the sky for 1-2 minutes. The object made no sound and had no wings or tail.
interesting points: The lights were the only distinguishing feature and seemed to move under intelligent control.
The phenomenon was visible in the sky for approximately 1-2 minutes.
There was no sound associated with the light, which was brighter than the surrounding stars.
The movement of the object was slow and erratic, not like an airplane.
The witness compared the object to other lights and airplane navigation lights they had seen, noting it was of a peculiar nature.
sighted object: a car-shaped craft with bluish green lights
